{
  "title": "Home IDS 🛡️ Tier 2: GeoIP & OSINT Intel",
  "uid": "ids-tier2-geo",
  "tags": ["ids", "tier2", "geo", "osint", "showcase"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "10s",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      { "name": "PROMETHEUS_DS", "type": "datasource", "query": "prometheus", "label": "Prometheus Source" },
      { "name": "LOKI_DS", "type": "datasource", "query": "loki", "label": "Loki Source" },
      { "name": "device", "type": "query", "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" }, "query": "label_values(home_ids_risk_score, hostname)", "refresh": 1, "includeAll": true, "customAllValue": ".*", "multi": false, "current": { "text": "All", "value": ".*" } }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 2, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🧭 [Triage Hub](/d/ids-master-hub-ultimate?var-device=${device}) | [📊 DNS & ML Diagnostics](/d/ids-tier2-dns/home-ids-tier-2-dns-ml-diagnostics?var-device=${device}) | [🔒 Network & Lateral (Zeek NDR)](/d/ids-tier2-ndr/home-ids-tier-2-network-lateral-zeek-ndr?var-device=${device}) | **🌍 GeoIP & OSINT Intel** | [⚙️ Engine System Health](/d/ids-system-health/home-ids-tier-2-engine-system-health)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "📖 Analyst Field Guide: Geolocation & Sandbox Correlation",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 2 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🚨 Threat: Threat Intelligence & Sandbox Detonations\n**How to hunt OSINT matches:** This dashboard skips AI guesswork and relies on absolute signatures from AlienVault OTX, AbuseIPDB, and VirusTotal.\n* 🟢 **Normal:** These panels should be completely flat at zero.\n* 🔴 **Threat Hunt:** A spike here is a guaranteed positive. A device on your network successfully resolved a known malicious payload dropper. Check the Loki logs to see exactly which domain/IP was flagged, then use the Geo Threat Map to verify if the server is hosted in a high-risk jurisdiction (e.g., RU, KP, IR)."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Threat Intelligence Feed Match Risk",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 7 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_ti_risk{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.5 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10, "lineWidth": 2 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "AbuseIPDB Reputation Threat Score",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 7 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_abuseipdb_risk{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 3 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10, "lineWidth": 2 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "VirusTotal Sandbox Analysis Hazard",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 7 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_virustotal_risk{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 3 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10, "lineWidth": 2 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "🔎 Filtered Workspace: OSINT & Threat Intel Forensics (Loki)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 15 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${LOKI_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "{job=\"home_ids_alerts\", environment=\"production\"} |~ \"(?i)threat intelligence|abuseipdb|virustotal\" | json | device_hostname=~\"$device\"" } ],
      "options": { "showLabels": false, "wrapLogMessage": true, "enableLogDetails": true }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "📖 Analyst Field Guide: Global Routing",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 23 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 📡 Global Infrastructure & Geographic Routing (Global Flow)\n**How to trace routing parameters:** Correlates external network endpoints back to their upstream routing providers (ASNs) and physical borders.\n* 🔴 **Threat Hunt:** Look for large red bubbles over high-risk jurisdictions on the map. If the 'Risk Magnitude by ASN' table lights up, an organization known for bulletproof hosting or ignoring abuse requests is heavily active on your network."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Risk Magnitude Allocation by ASN Matrix",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 27 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_asn_risk_score", "format": "table", "instant": true } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 4 } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Top External Target Routing Providers (ASN Volume)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 16, "x": 8, "y": 27 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "sum by (asn, org) (rate(home_ids_geo_traffic_total[5m]))", "legendFormat": "{{asn}} ({{org}})" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "fillOpacity": 0, "lineWidth": 1 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "geomap",
      "title": "Geo Threat Map (Coords)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 12, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 35 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "home_ids_geo_risk", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "A" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_geo_traffic_total", "format": "table", "instant": true, "refId": "B" }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        { "id": "joinByField", "options": { "byField": "latitude", "mode": "outer" } },
        { "id": "organize", "options": { "excludeByName": { "Time": true, "Time 1": true, "__name__": true, "__name__ 1": true } } }
      ],
      "options": {
        "view": { "id": "zero", "lat": 0, "lon": 0, "zoom": 1 },
        "controls": { "mouseWheelZoom": true, "showZoom": true },
        "layers": [
          {
            "type": "markers",
            "name": "Threat Layer",
            "location": { "mode": "coords", "latitude": "latitude", "longitude": "longitude" },
            "color": { "field": "Value #A" },
            "size": { "field": "Value #B", "min": 5, "max": 40 }
          }
        ]
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": [
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Value #A" }, "properties": [ { "id": "thresholds", "value": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 5 } ] } } ] }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "geomap",
      "title": "Threat Density (Country Code Lookup)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 12, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 35 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_country_threat_density", "format": "table", "instant": true } ],
      "options": {
        "view": { "id": "zero", "lat": 0, "lon": 0, "zoom": 1 },
        "controls": { "mouseWheelZoom": true, "showZoom": true },
        "layers": [
          {
            "type": "markers",
            "name": "Country Layer",
            "location": { "mode": "lookup", "lookup": "country" },
            "color": { "field": "Value" },
            "size": { "field": "Value", "min": 5, "max": 25 }
          }
        ]
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 }, { "color": "red", "value": 10 } ] } }
      }
    }
  ]
}